metadata.name: Manisha Portrait  V1
metadata.description:
Portrait artwork for Manisha, the main character of the comic series Manisha-Goddess of the Wild.

Manisha the Princess of Kimani is fighting for what she loves and tries to find her place in a world that is rapidly changing due to unpredictable events. The story takes place in Kimani a peaceful island with an astonishing nature located in the middle of the Sapphire Ocean.

Manisha is a creator owned story idea that was born out of an initial sketch. This artwork showed an opportunity and an entry into an unexplored world.

Digital Artwork signed and created 2022
